description: This cluster is used to manage basic commissioning lifecycle. This cluster also represents responsibilities related to commissioning that don’t well fit other com­ missioning clusters, like Section 11.9, “Network Commissioning Cluster”. It also hosts functionalities those other clusters may depend on. Matter Specification R1.3                        Connectivity Standards Alliance Document 23-27349 April 17, 2024
